org.apache.oodt.cas.cli.option

Class SimpleCmdLineOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.oodt.cas.cli.option.SimpleCmdLineOption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CmdLineOption
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActionCmdLineOption, AdvancedCmdLineOption, GroupCmdLineOption, HelpCmdLineOption, PrintSupportedActionsCmdLineOption

    public class SimpleCmdLineOption
extends Object
implements CmdLineOption
    CmdLineOption which implements the basic methods for any CmdLineOption. Can be used as-is or extends to add additional option features.
    Author:
    bfoster (Brian Foster)
